24:46.558 --> 24:47.559
Looks really important,

24:47.692 --> 24:49.295
so I didn't wanna,
like, scrumple it

24:49.428 --> 24:51.531
by shovin' it under the door
or leavin' out here

24:51.663 --> 24:52.530
or anything like that.

24:52.664 --> 24:53.865
You know, just in case.

24:53.999 --> 24:55.101
I see.

24:55.233 --> 24:57.001
