37:37.628 --> 37:38.596
Living room.

37:38.730 --> 37:40.733
Go on, then.

37:45.137 --> 37:46.538
Can you get that too, please?

37:46.670 --> 37:49.006
Okay.

37:58.215 --> 38:00.652
Wow!

38:03.820 --> 38:05.958
Yes.

38:10.360 --> 38:11.461
Who was it?

38:11.596 --> 38:13.231
Mailman.

38:13.364 --> 38:15.266
Fractions?

38:24.909 --> 38:27.645
I wish I could be
in the Seaview Ballet show.

