Iris.

44:02.246 --> 44:05.682
You okay, my darling?

44:05.817 --> 44:07.885
Oh.

44:15.527 --> 44:17.862
Oh!

44:19.630 --> 44:24.268
Well, I had a little friend
when I was about your age

44:24.402 --> 44:26.771
called Mr. Augustus.

44:28.505 --> 44:30.641
Oh, I suppose
that's rather old fashioned.

44:30.775 --> 44:31.576
Augustus?

44:31.710 --> 44:32.744
No, I love it!

44:36.447 --> 44:39.784
So, you gonna to tell me
what all this is about?

44:39.918 --> 44:41.452
I did it, Gran, like you said.

44:41.585 --> 44:43.253
I sent my wish out
to the universe

44:43.387 --> 44:44.456
and it came true.

44:44.588 --> 44:45.724
Look.

44:48.092 --> 44:51.028
Look, Gran,
it's The Royal Ballet.

44:51.163 --> 44:55.367
I... I have to audition,
so I practiced.

44:55.500 --> 44:57.534
A bit.

44:57.668 --> 44:58.769
Okay, a lot.

44:58.902 --> 45:01.171
I've gotten so much better,
I really have.

45:01.306 --> 45:03.007
You can learn anything
off YouTube.

45:03.139 --> 45:04.342
It's pretty cool.

45:04.476 --> 45:07.778
I can even do a pirouette now.

45:07.911 --> 45:09.913
Is that right?

45:10.047 --> 45:13.717
Well, I thought we agreed
that I would be your teacher

45:13.851 --> 45:15.420
and not Mrs. Goggle.

45:15.552 --> 45:17.521
Google, Gran, Google.

45:17.655 --> 45:19.057
Darling...

45:19.190 --> 45:23.794
you've got to be grown-up
and not be silly about this.

45:23.927 --> 45:25.528
You can't go off on your own

45:25.663 --> 45:28.900
dancing day in, day out
willy-nilly.

45:29.034 --> 45:32.603
It's dangerous, you know that.

45:32.737 --> 45:34.838
But I believe in it, Gran,
I really do.

45:34.972 --> 45:37.108
I believe in it,
and I know it's gonna happen.

45:37.240 --> 45:39.210
And that's great,

45:39.344 --> 45:42.213
but you've gotta get better,
too.

45:42.347 --> 45:43.581
Will you post it for me?

45:43.715 --> 45:44.782
Please?

45:44.916 --> 45:45.850
Please, Gran?

45:45.983 --> 45:48.085
I've got the address here.

45:48.219 --> 45:53.157
Well, I suppose I...

45:53.291 --> 45:55.994
I could send it off,

45:56.126 --> 45:59.764
but you've absolutely
got to swear not to tell on me.

45:59.898 --> 46:02.767
On Augustus's life.

46:04.768 --> 46:05.769
Shake on it?

46:24.422 --> 46:26.090
Close your eyes.

46:28.492 --> 46:31.929
Close them, no peeking.

46:32.061 --> 46:34.498
Now, deep breath.

46:36.266 --> 46:38.701
And focus.

46:41.472 --> 46:42.873
There you are!

46:43.007 --> 46:45.842
Oh, I see you!

46:47.411 --> 46:49.614
You're beautiful.

46:49.746 --> 46:54.184
Oh, my little dancing Iris.

47:03.994 --> 47:05.430
You're beautiful.

47:05.563 --> 47:08.231
Oh, Iris, can you see yourself?

47:08.365 --> 47:11.268
Oh, you're magical.

47:11.402 --> 47:13.905
That's my Iris.

47:14.038 --> 47:15.173
She's out there

47:15.306 --> 47:17.509
in the spotlight.

47:17.641 --> 47:20.477
Arabesque, arabesque,

47:20.610 --> 47:22.846
pirouette, pirouette.

47:22.981 --> 47:25.216
Pas de chat, pas de chat.

47:38.096 --> 47:39.797
Well, that's up to you.

47:41.731 --> 47:44.701
Look,
it's your decision completely.

47:45.969 --> 47:47.804
Oh, one second,
see that'll be Mum.

47:51.976 --> 47:53.311
Hello.

47:54.646 --> 47:57.581
She just has
to let me have more fun.

47:57.715 --> 47:58.883
Hmm.

47:59.016 --> 48:01.786
It's not easy being a mum,
you know?

48:01.918 --> 48:02.820
Iris?

48:04.320 --> 48:05.757
What is it?

48:05.889 --> 48:07.491
Iris, your heart.

48:07.625 --> 48:10.193
You've got a heart, sweetie.

48:10.327 --> 48:12.362
She's got a heart, Mum.

48:12.496 --> 48:14.231
Darling, don't forget the bags.

48:14.365 --> 48:17.369
We need to go right now
and we need to get to the car.

48:19.369 --> 48:21.371
Gran'll be right there with you.

48:21.505 --> 48:23.775
No need to worry,
little one, okay?

48:23.907 --> 48:24.775
Okay.

48:42.659 --> 48:44.127
Come on, come on, come on.

48:51.034 --> 48:52.036
Seatbelt, Iris.

49:06.751 --> 49:08.085
Oh, come, on,
where's your mum?

49:08.219 --> 49:09.086
Just go.

49:25.135 --> 49:26.338
There'll be another.

49:28.072 --> 49:29.407
Yeah.

49:30.474 --> 49:32.410
Can I go upstairs?

49:32.543 --> 49:33.510
Yeah.

49:33.644 --> 49:35.380
Yeah, I'll be up in a minute.

49:49.425 --> 49:51.594
How'd this happen?

49:51.728 --> 49:53.797
Apparently, it happens a lot.

49:55.565 --> 49:57.801
Could have been our only chance.

50:01.539 --> 50:03.674
Mum, please don't do that again.

50:03.807 --> 50:05.509
Stepping out in front
of the car like that,

50:05.643 --> 50:08.112
you could've been killed.

50:08.246 --> 50:09.480
The last thing
I need right now

50:09.614 --> 50:11.983
is my mum ending up
in hospital, too.

50:13.916 --> 50:15.485
Would've hurt more
if you'd gone all the way down

50:15.619 --> 50:17.688
without finding out.

50:53.291 --> 50:54.959
Iris, you in there?

50:58.362 --> 51:00.064
Iris?

51:00.197 --> 51:02.833
No parents allowed.

51:03.733 --> 51:05.002
Yeah, I can see that.

51:05.135 --> 51:07.905
Uh, can you come out here
for a second?

51:10.041 --> 51:11.376
Please?

51:11.509 --> 51:13.043
Password?

51:17.280 --> 51:19.483
Iris? Princess Iris?

51:22.719 --> 51:24.488
Penguins?

51:50.681 --> 51:52.851
I'm sorry about the false alarm.

51:54.284 --> 51:56.721
Must've been
really scary for you.

51:59.023 --> 52:01.692
You know you can talk
to me about anything.

52:01.826 --> 52:04.094
You can ask me anything.

52:05.663 --> 52:07.931
I do have a question, actually.

52:08.065 --> 52:10.969
Where will
my new heart come from?

52:12.737 --> 52:17.474
Well, when a child
doesn't need theirs anymore,

52:17.608 --> 52:19.443
they can give it away

52:19.577 --> 52:22.113
and it can live on
in someone else.

52:22.246 --> 52:25.249
That's what they call
an "organ donor."

52:25.382 --> 52:28.552
And one day, very soon,

52:28.686 --> 52:30.388
a little boy
or a little girl

52:30.521 --> 52:34.525
won't need their heart anymore
and they can give it to you,

52:34.657 --> 52:37.326
and you'll feel so much better.

52:37.460 --> 52:41.131
And will I still love you
if I have someone else's heart?

52:41.264 --> 52:43.934
Oh, darling.

52:44.068 --> 52:45.770
Yes, of course,

52:45.903 --> 52:49.039
you will always be you,
no matter what.

52:49.172 --> 52:53.710
You will always love us
just as we will always love you.

52:53.844 --> 52:56.280
And I'll still love dancing?

52:57.882 --> 53:00.217
I don't think there's anything
on this planet

53:00.351 --> 53:03.854
that could stop
Miss Iris Edwards from dancing.

53:05.521 --> 53:07.057
Thanks, Dad.

53:07.190 --> 53:10.593
Mr. Augustus
says you're welcome any time.

53:10.728 --> 53:12.363
Does he?

53:12.496 --> 53:14.964
Well, thank you,
Mr. Augustus.

53:18.168 --> 53:21.438
Right, um,
I'm gonna go now, sweetie,

53:21.572 --> 53:23.708
before I have a panic attack.

53:25.710 --> 53:26.742
Red, come in.

53:26.876 --> 53:28.746
I repeat, Red, come in.

53:28.878 --> 53:32.150
It's a code 1,
I repeat, it's a code 1.

53:47.565 --> 53:49.833
So, let me get this straight.

53:49.967 --> 53:52.702
You need an actual new heart.

53:52.836 --> 53:54.572
Apparently, mine doesn't work.

53:54.704 --> 53:56.039
That sucks.

53:56.172 --> 53:57.740
Quite a bit.

53:57.875 --> 53:59.342
Maybe you could have mine?

53:59.476 --> 54:01.179
I'm pretty sure you need that.

54:01.311 --> 54:03.947
I suppose.

54:12.389 --> 54:13.690
I just have to wait.

54:13.824 --> 54:15.259
I don't mind that so much,

54:15.393 --> 54:17.829
but how am I supposed
to become a dancer now?

54:32.175 --> 54:33.376
Um, can I help?

54:33.510 --> 54:36.847
Oh, um, you know, I...
I was lookin' for Audrey.

54:36.981 --> 54:40.117
Um, I...
I have something for her.

54:40.251 --> 54:41.485
Is she around?

54:41.619 --> 54:42.952
Uh, yeah, she's here, but
she's a bit busy at the moment.

54:43.086 --> 54:44.722
Uh, I can take it for her.

54:46.623 --> 54:47.925
Well, thanks, but I...

54:48.057 --> 54:49.226
you know, I'd rather
give it to her myself.

54:49.360 --> 54:51.796
Uh, she knows me,
you know, so...

54:53.362 --> 54:55.331
Yeah, no, I... I'll...
I'll come back later.

54:55.465 --> 54:56.401
Yeah, no worries.

55:56.327 --> 55:57.462
Brilliant.

56:04.034 --> 56:06.938
Um, I thought we paid this.

56:07.971 --> 56:09.306
I'll do it now.

56:09.440 --> 56:13.242
Um, they've just charged us £50
for it being late.

56:13.376 --> 56:15.679
I told you twice
to do this last week.

56:15.813 --> 56:18.548
Rather than tell me, why don't
you just do it yourself?

56:18.681 --> 56:20.450
Oh, sure, yeah.

56:20.583 --> 56:23.753
No, no, I... I'll just pull
13-hour-a-day shifts,

56:23.887 --> 56:25.289
and on top of that

56:25.422 --> 56:27.657
I'll just add some more things
to my list, and...

56:27.791 --> 56:29.059
Don't think
I wouldn't love

56:29.193 --> 56:31.762
to spend every day
runnin' around a farm.

56:31.894 --> 56:35.233
I work day and night
for this family.

56:37.067 --> 56:39.235
How foolish of me.

57:32.356 --> 57:33.491
Great.

57:59.583 --> 58:00.585
Brilliant.

58:03.586 --> 58:04.621
Red, it's yellow.

58:04.755 --> 58:06.490
Over.

58:06.623 --> 58:07.490
Yellow to red.

58:07.623 --> 58:09.525
Over.

58:09.659 --> 58:11.427
Go for Red.

58:11.561 --> 58:14.398
The target has been confirmed,
come to base now.

58:14.530 --> 58:16.799
Over.

58:16.932 --> 58:18.635
I repeat, come to base now.

58:18.768 --> 58:20.103
Over.

58:23.840 --> 58:25.175
Red?

58:25.643 --> 58:26.978
Red?

58:28.211 --> 58:31.081
Red, this is urgent.

58:46.697 --> 58:48.632
Hmm, temperature's up.

58:48.764 --> 58:50.000
How do you feel?

58:50.132 --> 58:53.002
Vision okay?
You feel faint?

58:53.137 --> 58:55.006
My feet hurt.

58:55.139 --> 58:56.907
Your feet?

58:58.242 --> 59:02.179
Oh my gosh, Iris,
your feet are so swollen!

59:02.311 --> 59:04.313
I'll call the doctor again.

59:04.447 --> 59:08.152
I don't wanna go back
to the hospital, I hate it.

59:16.693 --> 59:21.431
I know you don't feel like it,
but you need to eat something.

59:25.668 --> 59:28.504
Hmm, where's Iris gone?

59:28.637 --> 59:31.840
She's disappeared,
just this lumpy thing in here.

59:31.974 --> 59:33.476
Stop it.

59:33.610 --> 59:34.877
That's funny.

59:35.012 --> 59:38.516
I could've sworn
I heard something.

59:38.648 --> 59:39.949
Nope, don't think so.

59:40.083 --> 59:41.318
Stop it!

59:42.652 --> 59:46.088
Why is Daddy sleepin'
on the sofa?

59:46.222 --> 59:49.927
Oh, um, you know,

59:50.059 --> 59:51.894
I like to kick
in my sleep sometimes.

59:52.027 --> 59:53.262
Poor daddy.

59:54.931 --> 59:57.233
I'm tired.

