♪ Into it ♪

01:00:16.052 --> 01:00:19.489
♪ Into that deep blue abyss ♪

01:00:19.623 --> 01:00:22.092
♪ I don't mind ♪

01:00:22.224 --> 01:00:25.429
♪ 'Cause I got used to it ♪

01:00:25.561 --> 01:00:30.432
♪ It never really felt
that alone to me ♪

01:00:31.902 --> 01:00:35.472
♪ It never really felt
that alone ♪

