♪ I got it ♪

01:00:44.347 --> 01:00:47.651
♪ I got that feelin' again ♪

01:00:47.784 --> 01:00:50.387
♪ So I got out ♪

01:00:50.519 --> 01:00:53.856
♪ I put my windows down ♪

