01:01:28.157 --> 01:01:32.661
♪ To lose yourself completely ♪

01:01:34.398 --> 01:01:38.968
♪ And hang onto that feeling ♪

01:01:42.271 --> 01:01:44.708
♪ Don't let go ♪

01:01:57.052 --> 01:02:02.057
♪ And don't forget
